  defaultDialogue:
  - "Finally, it\u2019s happening. We\u2019re going to be free!"
  - We can escape!
  - "Together, we\u2019ll all be millionaires!"
  - You did great job, Tokyo.
  - "I didn\u2019t think things would go as planned \u2014 but we did it!"
  - Now, if you want to hear the full story of this robbery, talk to Moscow and then
    Oslo.
  - They know everything...
  - "I won\u2019t disturb you anymore."
  - "Go on \u2014 enjoy your freedom, your fortune... just enjoy it all!"
  - "But don\u2019t forget to put your mask on. Hehe..."
