  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 885bba7728ad07549a93f95d5f844caf, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialoguePanel: {fileID: 1095106980}
  NPCName: {fileID: 1935287521}
  playerInteractionPanel: {fileID: 293465029}
  dialogueText: {fileID: 1640801209}
  defaultDialogue:
  - Hey, so... you really want to know how it all started, huh?
  - "Well, it was all the Professor's idea \u2014 a perfect plan."
  - He brought together a group of people, each with nothing to lose, but everything
    to gain.
  - We weren't just robbers. We were a family.
  - Our goal? To break into the Royal Mint of Spain and print our own money.
  - No stealing from people. No violence. Just time, precision, and nerves of steel.
  - We trained for months, memorized every move, every detail.
  - "But of course, things didn\u2019t go exactly as planned..."
  - Tensions rose, feelings got involved, and outside, the police were breathing
    down our necks.
  - "Still, we stuck to the plan. Because walking out of there with billions \u2014
    that was worth it."
  inactiveDialogue:
  - Not now, sorry.
  relatedQuestName: Escape from the bank
  allowedQuestName: Escape from the bank
  contButton: {fileID: 430522730}
  wordSpeed: 0.03
  playerIsClose: 0
